, over their knowledge-market total:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\text{Share}_{p,t}^{k}\equiv\frac{\sum_{i\in p(t)}\alpha_{i}}{\sum_{i\in k(t)}\alpha_{i}}.
\]

\end_inset

Here, the notation 
\begin_inset Formula $i\in p(t)$
\end_inset

